  (text "TXS0108E LEVEL SHIFTER NOTES:\\nVCCA = 1V8_REF from JMISC B1 pin 4 (QRB2210 1.8V reference)\\nVCCB = +3V3 carrier rail\\nOE: 10kΩ pullup to VCCB (always-enabled)\\nBypass: 100nF on VCCA AND VCCB of each device within 2mm\\nU_LS1 channels: MPU GPIO 0-6 (7 channels used, 1 spare)\\nU_LS2 channels: MPU GPIO 7-11 + DSI_SW_SEL + spare\\nDSI_SW_SEL: 1.8V QRB2210 GPIO → 3.3V to CBTL04GP054 SEL pin\\nJ_MPU_GPIO header: 12-pin 2.54mm, 3.3V output\\nSilkscreen warning on J_MPU_GPIO: OUTPUTS ARE 3.3V ONLY (max 4mA)"
